plugins.ccuration.index
Class TermFileEntry

java.lang.Object
  plugins.ccuration.index.TermEntry
      plugins.ccuration.index.TermFileEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<TermEntry>
public class TermFileEntry
extends TermEntry

A TermEntry that associates a subject term with a final target FreenetURI that satisfies the term. NOTE: This is different to the code in Library! Most notably it is modifiable.

Author:
leuchtkaefer
